{"tid":437768,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍中心男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-10-16T09:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T09:58:01.000Z","uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc57b1883431bddbcd6a4ac34328a2aa4bd5dc9","tid":437768,"uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:47:06.000Z","msg":"西九龍中心發生墮樓事件，下午5時許，一名男子於商場內墮下，倒卧大堂，頭爆肢折當場死亡。警員接報到場，用帳篷將屍體蓋上，正調查其墮樓原因。"},{"pid":"4cc069c7a6fcb8e4a2b0417c04411a7fb771ab4a","tid":437768,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"又係西九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cd1cbea4a8fb3260f74764b2b6ee7a2429d820","tid":437768,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"深水埗軍營於1927年開始使用，軍營分為「南京軍營」和「銀禧軍營」，及至第二次世界大戰時，日軍攻佔香港，日軍把軍營改變為戰俘集中營，用以囚禁當時駐港而被俘虜的加拿大、印度和英國籍的士兵。第二次世界大戰後英軍重新使用深水埗軍營至1977年關閉，部分便建成了麗閣邨及深水埗公園。 <br />\n<br />\n而香港政府於1979年宣布香港成為「第一收容港」，軍營其餘的位置改建為「越南船民營」，而越南船民營於1989年11月關閉後，其位置建成了麗安邨、怡靖苑和西九龍中心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/l41260download2v137.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fl41260download2v137.jpeg&h=c0cba1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/z6649download3i137.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fz6649download3i137.jpeg&h=63f47a64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e41c41ea0d81af467bb1119fc7315466b97c1ea","tid":437768,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce9ec16712c2a4b1e898ea08e76e8945bc6f3692","tid":437768,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"又插穿網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}